information: Select Fruit sells French apples with a high visual and taste quality. Most Select Fruit apples are produced in our Val de Loire orchards (mainly in Maine & Loire). Select Fruit is the brandname of the Pom’évasion group which produces over 32 000 tons of apples and pears with over 600 hectares of orchards. Select Fruit is a selection of our best fruit.
address: 10 rue de la Fuye - PA de La Lanserre
